{"tid":1969654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"官員開會期間觀看許冠傑演唱會 林鄭：履行政府功能獲豁免","createTime":"2020-04-12T14:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T03:42:13.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"56eed66aa3b6f161c579c6c2182937d4a9151dfa","tid":1969654,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"特首下午與司局長開會　期間觀看許冠傑網上演唱會<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在社交專頁表示，下午與司局長及多名公務員開會，檢視疫情發展及商討第二輪「防疫抗疫基金」的具體安排，期間透過視像觀賞歌手許冠傑在網上演唱會，演唱歌曲《同舟共濟》。林鄭月娥說，由於開會屬履行政府功能，所以在禁止群組聚集規例下獲豁免，但期間都有採取預防措施，包括保持人與人之間的距離，亦全程佩戴口罩。許冠傑的演唱會製作團隊表示，透過網上觀看的總人數約為255萬。<br />\n<br />\n2020-04-12 21:24:25"},{"pid":"0a3cd1b6e08859645830f0de814433707daa62ab","tid":1969654,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:39:45.000Z","msg":"總之佢自己有金身, 同POPO+鄉黑係香港無敵, 強姦殺人貪污都無罪. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;特權階級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf334acbfb404f320d5a14ac9f81584dc6c8e05d","tid":1969654,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:40:16.000Z","msg":"明黑鳩 陳淑莊"},{"pid":"1e753e46f8af212eb827c2f5b6250cbaaea2e49d","tid":1969654,"uid":123308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DQF0RH9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDQF0RH9.jpg&h=6caac4f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港市民納稅畀公務員公僕娛樂睇片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed66e45d3de7f32986d2fc5c135752ce5c1f2e6","tid":1969654,"uid":126648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e753e46f8af212eb827c2f5b6250cbaaea2e49d","tid":1969654,"uid":123308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DQF0RH9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDQF0RH9.jpg&h=6caac4f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />